The CSS Crusaders

Availability for meeting expectations:
Flexible to be determined on a week by week basis.

Response time to communication expectations:
24 hours if pinged in the discord server

Definition of done: when is a task complete? (hint: "I'm done with that but I didn't check it in to github" is not done.):
When the tests are passed and the push is fully reviewed and pushed to the github main branch.

Scrum meeting format/frequency and distribution of documentation tasks (meeting minutes, updating task board):
Meet in discord call three times a week for ~30 minutes (depending on what will needed to be done). Everything for the meetings will be figured out on a trello board.

Procedure for adobting policies:
Simple majority for any new policies / removing all the bad policies.

Procedure for handling a member who is not meeting expectations:
1: Email them
2: Talk to them in lab
3: Physically corner them in lab

Signatures: each member must sign their name by typing their name at the bottom of the document.
Ennis Sonnen
